00:05:00.926 --> 00:05:05.847
LOVE IS AN IMPAIRMENT

00:05:19.569 --> 00:05:22.280
Be extra careful
not to irritate the wound.

00:05:23.657 --> 00:05:26.034
You have keloid-prone skin,

00:05:26.117 --> 00:05:29.204
so whenever you get injured,
the scars tend to rise up

00:05:29.287 --> 00:05:31.540
and spread beyond the original wound.

00:05:32.582 --> 00:05:35.418
You have sensitive skin
that reacts even to small wounds.

00:05:38.839 --> 00:05:43.134
With normal skin, this would have healed
without leaving a scar.

00:05:43.802 --> 00:05:47.055
But because your skin
forms aggressive keloids,

00:05:47.138 --> 00:05:49.140
it left noticeable scars like this.

