we chop their heads off

00:09:19.642 --> 00:09:22.687
and gracefully step
onto the newly arranged playing field

00:09:22.771 --> 00:09:24.898
and just keep doing what we've been doing.

00:09:24.981 --> 00:09:26.024
Sorry?

00:09:26.107 --> 00:09:27.901
They're just

00:09:28.485 --> 00:09:29.986
