00:09:51.174 --> 00:09:52.926
Those overpaid
former judges and prosecutors

00:09:53.009 --> 00:09:55.261
and advisors who can't land any clients.

00:09:55.345 --> 00:09:59.474
Who would follow a hatchet man
who swung their sword at them?

00:10:01.726 --> 00:10:02.727
