00:10:14.697 --> 00:10:15.573
Sadist?

00:10:17.283 --> 00:10:18.201
So?

00:10:18.701 --> 00:10:20.912
As it turns out, Ms. Seol Eun-yeong

00:10:20.995 --> 00:10:23.957
has keloid-prone skin,
which reacts severely to injuries.

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:27.127
What wouldn't leave a mark
on someone with normal skin,

00:10:27.210 --> 00:10:29.337
such as sexual activity,

00:10:29.420 --> 00:10:32.048
left keloidal scarring in Ms. Seol's case,
which gradually spread

00:10:32.132 --> 00:10:34.259
and has now become quite unsightly.

00:10:34.342 --> 00:10:36.177
On top of everything,

00:10:37.470 --> 00:10:38.638
she's a model.

00:10:41.224 --> 00:10:42.183
That's rough.

00:10:42.267 --> 00:10:43.226
