00:13:05.326 --> 00:13:07.745
When we fall in love,
we all lose a bit of judgment

00:13:07.829 --> 00:13:08.913
and become irrational.

00:13:08.997 --> 00:13:11.082
You've all been in love, right?

00:13:11.624 --> 00:13:14.002
Let's say you're at the beach in winter,

00:13:14.085 --> 00:13:17.130
