and body to the point

00:13:55.543 --> 00:13:57.920
where rational judgment
becomes impossible.

00:13:58.004 --> 00:14:01.007
So if the consent was given
under diminished capacity,

00:14:01.090 --> 00:14:02.300
it's not legally valid,

00:14:02.383 --> 00:14:04.677
and that makes it assault.

00:14:04.761 --> 00:14:07.221
