at the same time.

00:14:18.024 --> 00:14:19.233
No way.

00:14:19.942 --> 00:14:23.112
Are you seriously thinking
of going with this absurd argument?

00:14:23.696 --> 00:14:25.031
Since an assault charge requires

00:14:25.114 --> 00:14:27.742
grounds to invalidate the consent,

00:14:28.284 --> 00:14:31.496
we have no choice but to consider
Ms. Kang's argument more thoroughly.

